<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:21:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在商业航空经历了致命的一年之后，中国敦促进行安全评估</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</link><description>继2018年以来全球商业航空死亡人数最多的一年之后，中国当局呼吁对行业风险进行评估，以发现从航线到跑道的任何“隐藏”运营风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 05:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>受印度、韩国供应影响，新加坡 12 月航油进口量创多年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-dec-jet-fuel-imports-hit-multi-year-high-india-s-korea-supply-2025-01-03/</link><description>贸易消息人士和船舶追踪数据显示，新加坡的航空燃油进口量可能在去年 12 月创下多年来的新高，其中印度是最大的供应国，因为对欧洲的套利活动仍然关闭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-dec-jet-fuel-imports-hit-multi-year-high-india-s-korea-supply-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>2025年中国将大幅增加国债融资刺激经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</link><description>一位国家规划官员周五表示，随着北京加大财政刺激力度以振兴步履蹒跚的经济，中国将在 2025 年大幅增加超长期国债资金，以刺激商业投资和消费刺激计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉2024年中国销量逆势全球下滑创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-sales-rise-record-high-83000-december-2025-01-03/</link><description>美国电动汽车制造商特斯拉周五表示，其 2024 年销量将增长 8.8%，达到超过 657,000 辆的历史新高，在竞争激烈的市场中表现强劲，全球年度交付量首次下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-sales-rise-record-high-83000-december-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>海南免税消费大幅下滑，中国购物天堂陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</link><description>去年，由于经济疲软导致国内游客数量急剧下降，LVMH 和开云集团等全球奢侈品牌都在中国海南省开设了商店，免税支出下降了 29.3%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市上涨，美元创两年新高，美国利率上升，特朗普成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-03/</link><description>亚洲股市周五上涨，旨在摆脱 2025 年开局低迷的影响，而美元兑一篮子货币稳定在两年高点附近，因投资者担心美国利率在更长时间内保持较高水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>Skydance 和派拉蒙驳回对 84 亿美元合并计划的反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/skydance-paramount-dismiss-objections-planned-84-bln-merger-2025-01-03/</link><description>Skydance Media 和派拉蒙全球公司周四为其 84 亿美元的合并计划进行了辩护，敦促联邦通信委员会驳回批评者的反对意见，称其“毫无根据”且“毫无价值”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 00:45:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/skydance-paramount-dismiss-objections-planned-84-bln-merger-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，作为更广泛政策转变的一部分，中国央行可能在 2025 年降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-might-cut-interest-rates-current-level-15-2025-ft-reports-2025-01-03/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周五援引中国央行向该报发表的评论报道称，中国央行可能会在 2025 年“适当时候”将利率从目前 1.5% 的水平下调。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 00:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-might-cut-interest-rates-current-level-15-2025-ft-reports-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>英国立法者传唤 Shein 和 Temu 询问其劳工行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-summon-shein-temu-questioning-over-labour-practices-2025-01-02/</link><description>希望在伦敦上市的快时尚在线零售商 Shein 将于 1 月 7 日在英国举行听证会，英国议会委员会计划就这家 2008 年在中国成立的公司供应链中工人的权利提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 17:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-summon-shein-temu-questioning-over-labour-practices-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国提议进一步限制电池、关键矿产技术的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-proposes-further-export-curbs-battery-critical-minerals-tech-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四发布的一份文件显示，中国商务部已提议对一些用于制造电池组件和加工关键矿物锂和镓的技术实施出口限制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 15:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-proposes-further-export-curbs-battery-critical-minerals-tech-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于激励措施未能刺激需求，特斯拉年度交付量首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-posts-first-fall-annual-deliveries-demand-slows-2025-01-02/</link><description>特斯拉周四公布年度交付量首次下降，原因是埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)领导的电动汽车制造商老化的产品线提供了丰厚的年终激励措施，而新款 Cyber​​truck 皮卡未能吸引对高借贷成本保持警惕的客户。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 14:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-posts-first-fall-annual-deliveries-demand-slows-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>钴矿商 Jervois 达成救援协议以更好地与中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cobalt-miner-jervois-rescue-deal-after-struggle-compete-with-china-2025-01-02/</link><description>钴矿商 Jervois Global 周四表示，作为预先计划的破产程序的一部分，其一家贷方将将该公司私有化，这是随着中国竞争加剧而努力生存的最新一家西方矿商。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 13:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cobalt-miner-jervois-rescue-deal-after-struggle-compete-with-china-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车在挪威获得市场份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicles-gain-market-share-norway-2025-01-02/</link><description>挪威道路联合会 (OFV) 周四的数据显示，仅五年时间，中国电动汽车就已飙升至挪威新车销量的近 10%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 11:46:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicles-gain-market-share-norway-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：今年第一个交易日，需谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-02/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 11:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑制定限制或禁止中国无人机的潜在规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</link><description>美国商务部周四表示，正在考虑制定新规则，对中国无人机实施限制，以国家安全考虑为由限制或禁止中国无人机在美国销售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>